com.thedemgel.regions.data

Class UpdatedRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thedemgel.regions.data.UpdatedRegion

  • public class UpdatedRegion
extends Object
    The Object returned after a region is created or updated. Will return any positions that were not set, or if the region existed or not, and the region itself.
